Package: win11-window-tiling-gnome
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: dbus-x11 | dbus, bash, gnome-shell, gnome-shell-extensions | gnome-extensions, unzip
Maintainer: Local Build <local@localhost>
Description: Windows 11-style window tiling for Debian GNOME
 Installs and configures the Tiling Shell GNOME extension with Snap
 Assistant, Fancy Zones layouts, and Super+Arrow keyboard shortcuts.
 .
 Built specifically for Debian with GNOME. After install, run
 'win11-tiling-setup' and log out and back in.
